call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Edwards' (MIN) pass goes out of bounds.
Paul (GSW) brings his arms forward and releases away from Conley (MIN) on the perimeter. The contact that occurs is marginal.
Wiggins (GSW) slides his hand across Edwards' (MIN) front and marginal contact occurs at the start of the drive.
Saric (GSW) brings his hands toward Conley (MIN) and marginal contact occurs as Saric releases away to roll.
Conley (MIN) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Paul's (GSW) arm.
Conley (MIN) moves toward Looney (GSW) and brings his right arm outward as the screen is set. The contact that occurs is marginal as Looney attempts to move over the screen.

Looney (GSW) establishes himself in Conley's (MIN) path and does not deliver illegal contact during the pick. Looney takes a step back as a result of the initial contact and as both players release away from the pick, incidental foot to foot contact occurs and Conley loses his footing.
Gobert (MIN) cleanly blocks Saric's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Alexander-Walker (MIN) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Podziemski (GSW).
Saric (GSW) clamps and holds Anderson's (MIN) arm during the rebound.
